Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:07.13,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:34.69,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Controlling blood. That is my magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:38.02,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I cast that spell on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:42.12,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I've been able to manipulate \Nyour blood as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.08,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for your first task...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:48.92,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I shall force you to kill everyone \Nhere with your own two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:52.42,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Kill every last one of them perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:57.09,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta fell under the Queen of Witches' \Ncontrol and tried to kill his friends, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.55,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Make him stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:01.39,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:04.77,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot escape me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:09.27,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you are my daughter. My family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:11.27,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... part of your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.65,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.20,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.96,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A new spell activated, arising from \NVanessa's strong love for her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:32.54,main,queen,0000,0000,0000,,The red thread... of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:41.05,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Puppet's Blood has come undone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:45.56,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This magic only takes the side of myself \Nand those I have a family bond with.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.94,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have no bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:16.17,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(187,1)}I'm Home
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:26.24,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have no bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.46,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:35.46,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, look! \NI made a doll out of thread!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:41.09,flashback,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,My, it's so well-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:44.99,flashback,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make everyone smile with my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.85,flashback,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be able to, Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:58.39,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I obsessed so much over obtaining perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:04:01.47,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,that I forgot something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:09.37,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,There is a power you can obtain from \Nyour feelings {\i0}because{\i1} you're imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:13.24,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,The magic you could not\Nobtain under my care...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:16.29,italics,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,It came to you only because \Nyou were free and imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.67,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.42,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.68,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You have utterly defeated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:34.40,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Recovery Magic:\NCurse-Breaking Blood-Filled Cocoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds have healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.19,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.69,italics,Final,0000,0000,0000,,She fully healed all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.70,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of Witches really is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We... won?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:57.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,We won... We won because of your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.69,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:04.24,main,Fanzel,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:08.07,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.58,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how worried I was about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:12.07,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.03,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're naked, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:16.74,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? When did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.39,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:22.12,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:29.63,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.69,0:06:32.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.26,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.27,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,It's because all of you were there for \Nme that I was able to use that spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.40,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:51.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:53.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo! It doesn't hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt at all! Actually, \NI feel as light as a feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.97,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The moment he gets back on his feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:07.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Stupidsta! You're practically naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're bringing that up now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.24,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he took after you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.22,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But just look at me now, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:17.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I was healed, I felt like \Nmy muscles were even more powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.35,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,This bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.24,main,Witch 1,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness those violent \Npeople finally left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:41.37,main,Witch 2,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they get for \Nattacking the Witches' Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.87,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:50.27,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,was apparently looking for a \Nmagic stone that's in this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.01,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:56.62,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I would assume the magic \Nstone you speak of is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:08:00.47,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need of it. You may have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:02.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The magic stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:10.29,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! We got the \Nmagic stone just that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.28,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yami's gonna praise us for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:16.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it seemed like the Eye of \Nthe Midnight Sun wanted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:19.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, who the heck are they, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:23.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:28.96,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,That magic stone is a magical item \Nthat heightens the wearer's powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:32.63,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,but only those of the elf tribe\N are truly able to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:34.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.55,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,The elves possessed great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:44.23,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,They lived in what is now called the \NForsaken Realm several centuries ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:48.11,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Each individual elf had an extraordinary \Namount of magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:52.02,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Many of them were equal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.11,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Several centuries? Lady, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.78,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Your skin is way too flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.17,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:05.12,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,The humans outnumbered them, and when \Nthey fought them, the elves were annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.54,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,That Fana girl's third eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.88,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,That is forbidden magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:18.51,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,But that girl wasn't the one who \Nactivated that spell. It was someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:22.64,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary humans are unable to \Nmeddle with forbidden magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:25.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:27.19,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,Activating a forbidden spell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:32.17,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,requires a tremendous amount of \Nmana and some sort of sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:36.21,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,The ancient demon was also \Na top-level forbidden spell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:38.95,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,activated by the leader of the elf clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.92,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:51.71,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,It could be that the Eye of the Midnight Sun\Nare descendants of the elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:53.71,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:58.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me the evil \Nmonsters from the picture book
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,my nanny read to me as a\N child were actually elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:04.83,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! We're getting a \Nton of amazing new intel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.69,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting! I'm gonna \Nbecome a reporting fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:12.93,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,And Asta, the two swords you bear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:17.83,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,They are the ruined remains of the \Nmagic swords used by the elves' leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:22.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:26.54,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asta's head exploded because he couldn't \Nkeep up with the conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Stupidsta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.42,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He can't! He's too dumb to \Nhandle any more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:37.09,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to fight them, that mystery \Nshould also be resolved eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:40.05,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:47.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So you're really going back \Nto the Diamond Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.43,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:53.67,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen of Witches sealed the effects \Nof Puppet's Blood into this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:57.72,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass it off as some longevity \Ndrug and give it to the king,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.94,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,and put an end to Morris's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:04.95,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll remake the Diamond Kingdom\N into a peaceful nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:08.80,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that I'll help Mars out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:14.63,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,That seems like the quickest way to get into \Nthe top ranks of the Diamond Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.34,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, can we trust this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.92,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become someone you can approve of,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:24.72,italics,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,and one day I'll come to \Nvisit you again, Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.81,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep Fana with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.64,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Mars, Ladros, don't push yourselves too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.28,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. We'll take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:36.65,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to make sure she doesn't \Nhave to see Master naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:41.40,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Fana, I'm sorry. Please wait\N until I've changed the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.51,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I'll make the Diamond Kingdom \Nthe sort of place you can return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.08,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait as long as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:56.35,main,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Diamond Kingdom is peaceful, \Nlet's go see the world together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.67,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.63,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, one day, that'll be you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.55,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:08.95,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,You called me a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:14.27,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,If you run into trouble, I'll come help \Nyou at any time, no matter where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:18.11,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,That's what friends are for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever need any help, let me know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blast my way right \Ninto the Diamond Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.83,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.63,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,But this is still your birthplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.59,main,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,You may come to visit whenever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:56.24,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,If I start at number two,\NI'll be at the top in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:59.65,main,Domina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't forget to support Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:01.91,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.94,main,Mariella,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:10.00,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished your goodbyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:13.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get the heck out of this creepy forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:19.07,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man... I didn't have a chance \Nto get close to any of the witchies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:22.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.77,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for healing Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.73,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,See you again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:35.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami! My arms are fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We actually made it back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:38.98,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to everyone, I'm healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.27,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:43.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you half-naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:46.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:50.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami! We found a magic stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.91,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, kid. Here's your first mission \Nsince getting your arms fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.42,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Go get me some booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.46,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll go at maximum speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:04.30,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, the others aren't back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? They probably dropped \Ndead in a ditch somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:08.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:13.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. If you don't want \Nto die too, get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:14.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.39,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:23.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yo. Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.22,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I bought you some!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:39.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That really was fast. Talk about creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So what's my next mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're working too much. \NNo more missions for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Also, put some damn clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:57.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No way... If you take my missions \Naway from me, what do I have left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.02,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:02.15,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. You don't need to cry that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:05.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I brought you some clothes. \NHurry up and put them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.40,main,Manga,0000,0000,0000,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.98,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's Magna's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:17.51,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Magna and Luck went to \Na dungeon to find a way to fix my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:19.16,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta thank them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:27.80,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! \NSomething crazy happened to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:32.91,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Fallen angel who lost your wings... \NIn order to see you smile again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.39,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,we traveled to a dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.12,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We were lost in the dark, drowning in despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.79,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,and my heart came close \Nto breaking many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:43.02,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,But every time that happened, \NI would see a vision of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:47.54,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You shook my soul. I killed my \Nweaker self and continued fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.76,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Did his personality completely change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:52.64,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The mana is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.32,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:59.54,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We wandered the dungeon, disposed of \Nour enemies, and I became more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.79,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,But there was just one important \Nthing I couldn't find:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:06.04,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,a spell to heal the wounds \Nthat torment you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Powerless and defeated, I had to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.27,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The mana is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:14.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my arms are fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:20.60,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Well, \Ngood for you, you little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.31,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Asta! Now let's kill each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:25.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.52,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.80,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:34.09,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Gauche and Gordon also went \Nto the royal library to fix my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.49,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:40.62,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! They turned into nerds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:44.14,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I have awakened to the splendor of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.79,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful spell arrays are like paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.14,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Master Gordon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.75,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, why did your \Npersonality change, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:57.43,sign_24357_235_Magic_truly_is_t,Sign/Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Magic truly is the ultimate artistic masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:57.43,italicstop,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I still have no idea what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:00.96,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, we still haven't found a \Ncure for your arms, Master Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.98,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long it takes,\Nwe'll find a way to remove the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, please wait, \Nplease wait, I implore you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my arms are fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:15.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, you little punk?! \NI said I'd fix them someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:18.29,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Go get yourself cursed again, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose is bleeding, Gauche!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.39,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It's from rage, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:28.83,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.94,sign_25255_248_I_know___,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.94,sign_25255_248_I_know___,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,That your nose only bleeds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:37.19,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,when you wish really hard for someone\N important to you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:41.57,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that because this was the first time\N we'd ever been alone together for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:46.83,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This might be the way to cure Asta's arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.89,flashback,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, that won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:52.38,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,It always happens when you\N think about your little sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:56.09,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,but your nose was secretly bleeding when\N you were thinking about Asta, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:02.37,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This is dumb. I'm going \Nto stare at Marie now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.10,sign_25255_248_I_know___,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,You actually care about Asta
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.85,sign_25365_250_when_you_wish_re,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,just as much as you care for your little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:11.65,sign_24357_235_Magic_truly_is_t,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,Just like your sister, yes, Asta is family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:15.44,sign_24357_235_Magic_truly_is_t,Gordon/sign,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that since I'm Asta's\Nbest friend, I'm also your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.61,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Charmy—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.56,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.56,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, it's me, Charmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.10,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I got infested with magic mushroom parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.02,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be eating those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:38.57,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I can't transform properly! \NThis is so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:40.90,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Should you really be embarrassed right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:44.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Charmy! Don't eat any more of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:46.71,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:49.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You ate one, and three more sprouted up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.59,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Here, try one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.90,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I picked lots of other yummy things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You risked your lives for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:05.04,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sorry... We couldn't \Nfind a way to fix your arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.23,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:12.68,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,You're cured! How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:14.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's really nothing \Nembarrassing about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like we've got \Nplenty of food and drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:24.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making muscle-for-brains \Nover there take a break,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,so let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.87,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Party time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:35.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice to be able to eat with my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:40.62,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, since no one was around this morning, \NI didn't get to feed them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:41.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:48.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You guys must be starving. \NDon't worry, I've got plenty for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:55.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course this happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:58.18,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. No one's done the laundry, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:01.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I supposed to hang all these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:04.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,No one's cleaned the place, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:10.90,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:11.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:18.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of toilet paper. Go get me some.\N And who told you to open the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:21.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And on to the next!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.67,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The captain told him to rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.31,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,but he's not getting a chance to rest at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:37.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure that's fine for Stupidsta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:45.32,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... This is where I feel most at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.66,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,To to mention—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:54.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:58.42,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I found in the outside world
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:01.99,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,is my other family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:38.48,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.82,0:22:37.78,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:41.98,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}I Wonder Why
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.12,0:22:40.95,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I Wonder Why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:44.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:50.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why Fana doesn't get burned \Nwhen Salamander is covered in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:51.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because it's magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:56.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why your clothes don't get \Nwet inside the Sea Dragon's Lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:23:02.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't konbu seaweed \Nflavor the ocean like dashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:05.86,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Leave any food questions \Nto me, Professor Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:11.01,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,The component that gives konbu dashi its \Nflavor, glutamic acid, lies within its cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:13.69,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Those cells have what's called \N"selective permeability,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:16.01,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,which gives it the ability \Nto take in what's necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:17.76,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,and get rid of everything it doesn't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:21.55,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,The glutamic acid that creates the dashi \Nin konbu is necessary for its survival,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:24.80,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,so it doesn't leave its cells while \Nit's still alive within the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:27.66,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,But once it dies and is dried, \Nthe cells break apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:30.03,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,causing the glutamic acid to come out,\N which turns into dashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:33.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Stupidsta's \Ngoing to understand any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:37.03,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:40.07,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely going to strike \Nagain so they can get the magic stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:42.95,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what are they after?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:47.60,main,vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 66: "The Eye \Nof the Midnight Sun's Secret."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:23:50.14,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 66\N\N{\fs18} The Eye of the Midnight Sun's Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.60,0:23:49.87,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Being a heavy drinker is my magic!
